   "author_association" : "MEMBER",
   "body" : "This PR allows to cross-compile as follows:\r\n- on Intel-based macOS 11.4:\r\n```\r\n% make -C depends HOST=arm64-apple-darwin20\r\n% CONFIG_SITE=$PWD/depends/arm64-apple-darwin20/share/config.site ./configure\r\n% make\r\n```\r\n\r\n- on M1-based macOS:\r\n```\r\n% make -C depends HOST=x86_64-apple-darwin18 NO_QT=1\r\n% CONFIG_SITE=$PWD/depends/x86_64-apple-darwin18/share/config.site ./configure\r\n% make\r\n```\r\n\r\nTo cross-compile on M1-based macOS without `NO_QT=1`, see a followup #22487.\r\n\r\nThis PR:\r\n- cherry-picked two commits from #21851 which goal is cross-compiling on Linux systems\r\n- is based on #22448\r\n\r\nNo behavior changes for other builder-host pairs.",
